{"type": "article", "id": 60113, "title": "辛芷蕾演绎 lululemon 新年系列，支付宝年度账单是一张小票 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2019-01-09T05:51:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 55783, "name": "账单"}, {"id": 123, "name": "咖啡"}, {"id": 8367, "name": "lululemon"}, {"id": 2399, "name": "支付宝"}, {"id": 2608, "name": "BMW"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 12, "praise_count": 40, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190109132106frpF2odYGwzCtKxb.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p line=\"FBD7\"><a href=\"https://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/ryan-reynolds-named-face-of-armani-code-scent-1202950550/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Ryan Reynolds 成为 Armani Code 香水全新代言人，</b></a>之前代言人是 Chris Pine。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109132145PdUuz9sE4amrBjTn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.648438\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p line=\"NYID\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA4NzM0MjU3MA==&amp;mid=2651177955&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=2a3326e7aef53e86fb478106fb8853b0&amp;chksm=8bcb8f66bcbc06700f79a0396459037cb74f778faab6ff1379841e90057b30816e804a5ecc4a&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0109OIhDPQEZHqc6I5bomOLI&amp;key=6e3ec9351776f4c122ef9e1db5665a7693321dd458c962f5c807d896a3edf3fcd8c0041bac3969dc0f1a2b4ba6e26189c2086890ae256c8325927a3cd68c7e1311b0e3954ab5621b4472b9d6fa7594d1&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=DmzE5C%2FFYrmSB5a%2BmZlUrN9dB9uOpl8PwBCkqMEjonjP73gApt3MajO9kEUGDjG3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">lululemon 和演员辛芷蕾联合推出“亚洲特别系列”，</a>该系列为春节限量发售，将中国传统刺绣艺术和古典印花融合。她作为新的社区伙伴，在片中展现了健康身材。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\"> \t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=y082251v8qn\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe> \t</figure> \t</div><h3>又是跨界</h3><p line=\"WUiN\"><b>故宫和<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4326197586100898?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">中国工商银行</a>、<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/1907753765/4325973295458049\" rel=\"nofollow\">民生银行</a>合作推出银行卡，</b>卡片设计有人物、建筑、符牌、仙鹤、锦鲤、龙袍等主题。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109132240nbrsJEiaofS7BItR.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.567621\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109132240QgR1rHZsDShUwCNW.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.567621\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109132241eh1caHWBdyCGLKVm.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.567621\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109132241caLmFK9UtBHdJYxe.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.567621\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109132346NxKPaSdJIncDQ9uA.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109132320T7AGq2x8SQ5ml9hg.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109132321D3VUeEMvxJcgRyBX.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109132321IUlS5LAtVyvOeqxz.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109132319W7TGPMcL8JZFeNdD.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109132319Yjvlc2ydA83XT4eB.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109132320yvzJ8tX6FGQHak2C.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109132320z8ohvN27VgcJTIpH.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><p line=\"SFY8\"><a href=\"https://news.mattel.com/news/mattel-announces-global-licensing-agreement-with-global-boy-band-bts\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">美泰宣布将和韩国男团防弹少年团（BTS）合作，</a>将为防弹少年团制作玩偶、珍藏手办、玩具套装、游戏等商品。不过许多粉丝翻出了美泰与 One Direction 等艺人合作的成品后，担心起“防弹娃娃”的最终模样。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109132421ikQE0raZKyI34RnW.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.826984\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><h3>值得一看的 Case</h3><p line=\"3wjL\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4326191454203210?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>支付宝年度账单可以查看了，</b></a>今年支付宝特意把账单设计成了小票形式。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109132447mnOCX3z9Hdbie6Rh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109132448Yrot9FdiufRg0N52.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p line=\"eKUE\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4326223846514544?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>天猫 Tmall Discovery 化用“东方快车谋杀案”、“恐怖童谣”、和“头文字 D” 等情节，设计了几桩悬疑案件。</b></a>咖啡豆是事件中的主人公，离奇被“谋杀”，引出“花式续命”的主题为年轻人推荐热门咖啡品类的商品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\"> \t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=x0823442p05\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe> \t</figure> \t</div><p line=\"CJjy\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4325977230109138?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>天猫通发布了“新·新年 更有范儿”的广告片，代言人易烊千玺出演。</b></a>片中的三个故事，家人们在老人和小朋友之间巧妙切换。任何年纪，家人都能团聚在一起。这次营销活动是天猫为了农历年购物街活动打造。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\"> \t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=f0824ooa5cx\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe> \t</figure> \t</div><p line=\"Kk7S\">宝马新代理商 Goodby，Silverstein＆Partners 为宝马制作的广告内容，都来自于之前的代理商 KBS。<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sbPQNv4HMYo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">这样操作是因为活动是针对认证过的宝马旧车，</a>视频内容相同，但是新广告重新配音：演员 Chris Pine 还在每个地点加入了一些新评论。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\"> \t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=i08256b51ki\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe> \t</figure> \t</div><p line=\"3xLT\">星巴克中国将于 1 月 11 日迎来 20 年生日，<a href=\"http:// https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/8y7K2QhW310k6a8YabItvA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>推出制作专属自己的“20 岁”海报活动，</b></a>在 H5 页面的 3 个问题也围绕着年轻的 20 岁展开。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190109132624tKnlfLsWCQrk4A1U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.581333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>其他，也很重要</h3><p line=\"vrXz\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3ODgwNTAzNw==&amp;mid=2659020544&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=9b55a0558586ab3bcbad748bbc26e0ea&amp;chksm=8434ee42b34367544e65778457469c88769442d3f329032a572dcd1dbfd81b22142365e0110c&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=01086PpIyU5l18xTtp8uyJie&amp;key=ad91e5c59693255a39d5b00b6c57af3faaba88783238f9b350a6883f6bf84e03bf5e67aa755ffd4f5c9e494cd0e569f218653242acb78586531b4a988f1a94bb8052734c9415d7f04d6b9eeeb09fb67c&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=DmzE5C%2FFYrmSB5a%2BmZlUrN9dB9uOpl8PwBCkqMEjonjP73gApt3MajO9kEUGDjG3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>微信发起用户最喜爱的朋友圈广告年度评选，</b></a>目前排名前三的分别是偶像团体出演的 I DO 广告，杜江和霍思燕夫妇参演的 Tiffany 和爱彼迎的曼谷“萨瓦迪卡”。</p><p line=\"0kvS\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4326279174452249?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>微博管理员账号发布关于调整微博转发评论数据显示方式的公告，</b></a>遏制数据造假的问题。</p><p line=\"bWlR\">从今年 1 月底开始，微博站方将对微博转发、评论计数显示方式进行调整：微博转发、评论计数显示上限均为 100 万，当实际数量超过 100 万时，均显示为 100 万+。</p><p line=\"hBhQ\">媒体账号和政务账号因账号属性不在此次调整之列。</p><p line=\"I3sF\"><a href=\"https://adage.com/article/the-viral-video-chart/viral-video-chart-12-3-18/315840/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Google “小鬼当家重现“广告片的观看量在圣诞广告中排第一，</b></a>已经获得 7070 万次观看。该广告是为了推广 Google 的人工智能语音助理。</p><p line=\"SRv2\"><a href=\"https://www.adweek.com/programmatic/verizon-media-and-microsoft-ink-global-native-advertising-deal/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Verizon Media 与微软达成全球原生广告协议，</a>协议主要是多广告位投放，前者承诺将为微软提供独特的媒体广告和新兴投放广告的渠道。</p><p line=\"nRcj\">从 1 月 10 日到 17 日，淘宝直播将在广东、重庆、山东等地连续七天举办<b>“年味中国·县长来了”主题的直播</b>。各地县长将联合淘宝主播直播销售家乡土特产。</p><p line=\"4UZf\" style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: inherit; text-align: left;\">题图来自：Pixabay @</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: inherit; font-family: Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 冬青黑, STXihei, 华文细黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, Helvetica, Tahoma, &quot;Arial sans-serif&quot;; text-align: left;\">stevepb</span></p>"}